{
  "stem": "17720.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 139.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, this was actually one very special moment in the history of Bulgarian people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They really received them like people that free them, that bring open one page of their life with new hopes, hopes for a better life.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Perhaps this always happened in the human history, when some changes occur.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The people of lower classes, many times, accept this with one very positive attitude with hopes that this change will bring something good in their life.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So, in this situation it was not much different.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know how much good the new era was bringing to the life of Bulgarians.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But nevertheless, the new era came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was the era of socialism in Bulgaria.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now later on the history proved that it brought not much better things in their life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the 9th of September, 1944.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is the day that's really definitely the life of the Jewish people was saved, it was known that they will be not deported.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And these iron ferryboats were again relocated in their normal place there in the ports.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [SIGHS] Very soon after that, we returned back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My family, after approximately one year that we arrived to Vidin, separate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was taken in hard labor [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [? fit-- ?] locations, location of hard labor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said-- they stayed separated until the end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was taken somewhere in the uranium mines, where they were working the uranium from the earth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was places where they used to send, in peaceful time, the people who are condemned to execution, because of the radiations.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So, this is what happened at the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I saw my father after the 9th of September.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
